                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a01">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#138v"/>: An Asmat Prayer for protection against demons, an Arabic text written in Gə‘əz characters.
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">የጋኔን፡ የማስቀርብ፡ ቢስምላሒ፡ አርማኒ፡ እራሒም፡ ለሚኩኒ፡ አለዚነ፡ ከፈሩ፡ ምን፡ አህሊል፡ ኪታቤ፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a02">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto)"/>": Note of secondary ownership, in purple ink and blue ink
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e01">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iv(erso) #iir(ecto) #126rv #139r #139v #140r"/>: blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e02">
                    <desc>
                    Identified in the insurance hand list as Psalter 22
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e03">
                    <desc>
                    Navigation system:
                    green yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#15 #32 #45 #70"/>;
                    black yarn is sewn into fore edge of <locus target="#23"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e04">
                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 5 (incorrectly numbered on <locus target="#49r"/>) and 12
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e05">
                    <desc>
                    Space was left on Psalm 118 for the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters, but they were not written
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e06">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#4v #5r #6r #9v #10v"/>, etc.);
                    and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#12v #14r #19r #23v #24v"/>, etc.);
                    and in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#121v"/>, line 14);
                    erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#100r"/>);
                    text has been removed (<locus target="#17v #26r #28r #35r #44r"/>, etc.)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
